<script>
    import axios from "axios";

    export default {
        name: "Report",
        data() {
            return {
                report: {},
            };
        },
        created() {
            this.getData();
        },
        methods: {
            getData() {
            axios
                .get("https://api.github.com/users/luizmedeiros00")
                .then((res) => {
                    this.user = res.data;
                })
                .catch((error) => {
                    console.log(error);
                });
            },
        },
    };
</script>
